room_title: Escape room "Circus of the Stranded" by Brainstorm Escapes: The Conspiratory in Champaign-Urbana
room_description: The Cirque Du Sourire is one of the worst circuses in the world. The games are rigged, the animals are sick, the music is dreadful, and the workers are held against their will under contract! The evil Ringmaster Monstre has arranged his freak show to be the best one around but because of the terrible conditions, all of the freaks want out of the deal. It is up to your group to set them free!
